### Get reminders for a customer
GET http://localhost:5000/api/reminders/customer/6a1c51a084eee56df6004781

### Schedule a new reminder
POST http://localhost:5000/api/reminders
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "customerId": "6a1c51a084eee56df6004781",
    "scheduledDate": "2026-05-31T20:42:00",
    "message": "Dear customer, this is a reminder to clear your pending dues.",
    "channel": "whatsapp"
}

### Send reminder immediately (manual trigger)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/reminders/6a1c4c71de0edc78040089dc/send-now

### Cancel a scheduled reminder
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/reminders/6a1c4c71de0edc78040089dc



### Reminders will schedule every 3 days for this customer
POST http://localhost:5000/api/reminders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Amit Sharma",
  "phone": "+919999888877",
  "email": "amit.sharma@example.com",
  "address": "Flat 102, Sector 15, Noida",
  "reminderIntervalDays": 3
}